videos.description: Ben Dinucci's 33-yard touchdown pass to Jester Weah gives Pitt the early lead.
videos.headline: Dinucci finds wide open Weah for a Pitt TD

videos.description: Nyheim Hines sprints past the Pitt defense for an 83-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Hines takes off for 83-yard TD

videos.description: Nyheim Hines strikes again with a speedy 92-yard punt return for a touchdown.
videos.headline: NC State's Hines goes untouched on punt return TD

videos.description: Big offensive lineman Brian O'Neill takes a throwback pass all the way down to the 1-yard line which leads to a Pitt touchdown.
videos.headline: Dinucci finds O-lineman Brian O'Neill who rumbles down to the 1-yard line

videos.description: Mike Stevens picks off Ben Dinucci with an athletic grab.
videos.headline: Stevens makes nice pick for Wolfpack

videos.description: Ryan Finley finds Jakobi Meyers in the back of the end zone to give N.C. State the lead.
videos.headline: Finley fires a strike to Meyers for Wolfpack TD

videos.description: Kelvin Harmon does his best Randy Moss impression with a crazy catch that leads to a Wolfpack touchdown.
videos.headline: Jackson gets Mossed as Harmon goes up and gets it

videos.description: Jaylen Samuels takes off for a 40-yard touchdown to seal the win.
videos.headline: Samuels ices the game for N.C. State
